snippet: Authorities say they've seized dozens of guns, thousands of rounds of ammunition and police equipment including badges, silencers and vehicles from the home of a man who tried to pull over a uniformed officer as he drove to work....

headline.print_headline: Guns Seized From Ohio Police Impersonation Suspect
headline.main: Guns Seized From Ohio Police Impersonation Suspect

lead_paragraph: Authorities say they've seized dozens of guns, thousands of rounds of ammunition and police equipment including badges, silencers and vehicles from the home of a man who tried to pull over a uniformed officer as he drove to work.
